---

---

<section id="start-here" class="py-28 md:py-36 px-6 md:px-16 bg-sand-deep/40">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2
        class="font-headline text-basalt text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.02] tracking-tight"
      >
        Start <em class="italic text-ochre">here</em>.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <a
        href="/getting-here"
        class="reveal group bg-sand-bright p-8 md:p-10 border border-basalt/10 hover:border-ochre/30 transition-all"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-ochre font-bold mb-4"
        >
          How to Get Here
        </h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[15px] text-basalt/75 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Pohnpei International Airport (PNI) is connected to Honolulu and Guam
          via United Airlines' Island Hopper — the only scheduled route. Most
          visitors fly through Guam. US citizens don't need a visa.
        </p>
        <span
          class="font-label text-ochre text-xs tracking-[0.14em] uppercase font-semibold flex items-center gap-3 group-hover:gap-5 transition-all"
        >
          Getting here
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-ochre transition-all group-hover:w-14"></span>
          <span class="font-body text-base">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/places-to-stay"
        class="reveal group bg-sand-bright p-8 md:p-10 border border-basalt/10 hover:border-ochre/30 transition-all"
        style="transition-delay: 0.1s;"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-ochre font-bold mb-4"
        >
          Where to Stay
        </h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[15px] text-basalt/75 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Small hotels in Kolonia, a handful of guesthouses, and a few Airbnbs.
          No chain resorts — that's the point. Book early; options are limited.
        </p>
        <span
          class="font-label text-ochre text-xs tracking-[0.14em] uppercase font-semibold flex items-center gap-3 group-hover:gap-5 transition-all"
        >
          Places to stay
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-ochre transition-all group-hover:w-14"></span>
          <span class="font-body text-base">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/travel-info"
        class="reveal group bg-sand-bright p-8 md:p-10 border border-basalt/10 hover:border-ochre/30 transition-all"
        style="transition-delay: 0.2s;"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-ochre font-bold mb-4"
        >
          When to Come
        </h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[15px] text-basalt/75 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Pohnpei is warm and wet year-round (80–88°F). December through March
          is slightly drier. The island never gets crowded. Dive conditions are
          good all year.
        </p>
        <span
          class="font-label text-ochre text-xs tracking-[0.14em] uppercase font-semibold flex items-center gap-3 group-hover:gap-5 transition-all"
        >
          Travel info
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-ochre transition-all group-hover:w-14"></span>
          <span class="font-body text-base">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/travel-info#us-visitors"
        class="reveal group bg-sand-bright p-8 md:p-10 border border-basalt/10 hover:border-ochre/30 transition-all"
        style="transition-delay: 0.3s;"
      >
        <h3
          class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-ochre font-bold mb-4"
        >
          For US Visitors
        </h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[15px] text-basalt/75 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Under the Compact of Free Association (COFA), US citizens can live,
          work, and travel freely in the FSM. No visa. No special permits.
          Pohnpei is closer to the US than most people think.
        </p>
        <span
          class="font-label text-ochre text-xs tracking-[0.14em] uppercase font-semibold flex items-center gap-3 group-hover:gap-5 transition-all"
        >
          US visitor guide
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-ochre transition-all group-hover:w-14"></span>
          <span class="font-body text-base">→</span>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
